message.body: Hey Britt! Its Dan. Good to hear from u
Hey you! I did still have your number. I was gonna text you but I figured it wasn't the same number anymore. So instead of having an awkward convo with a
stranger, I figured Facebook message was safer
Haha yea I'm a loyal Verizon customer. Same number forever. How r u?
I'm doing great. Working right now. What about you? How are thing?
glad to hear. I'm good. Are you a lawyer now?
Nah. I thought about it alot and decided I hated law now. The more I got into the more depressed I got. So I work at a mortgage company now, about to bec
ome a loan officer
Where are u located?
It's in fort Washington
You live in Lansdale still?
Yeah. Well, north wales, but same thing. I think I'm moving to manayunk in like a month tho
Oh snap. You mean danayunk though. I live in center city philly now
Hahahha my bad, Danayunk. Although I think they'll quickly rename it when I get there. And that's awesome. That's not far from "Danayunk" what are you do
ing its yourself now?
I am a budget analyst for the philly school district for my career. Boring day today!
Hahah Awww well that's ok. Boring days sometimes lead to epic weekends
Lol yea man the weekend has Already started in my head lol
Lord help them when 5 pm rolls around. That's the hour of wild disregard for life lol
lol I heard that. Its freakin gorgeous out too. Might run home naked. What r u up to this weekend?
Hahahah naked huh? And which route do you take home? Lol
And not sure about tonight, but probably going to ocean city Maryland tomorrow for the weekend
I live 3 blocks from work..its glorious
Damn ocmd! Living it up!!
Hahahah that's awesome. I'm jealous
Trying to. It's been a rough couple weeks. Trying to get back to fun times now
No better time for fun than the summer!!
Damn right
What are you getting into this weekend?
I have a family reunion tomorrow. no plans Sunday yet
Sounds fun. And tonight?
Gonna go home. Cuz the reunion is so far away
Gotcha. Well have a great time
Thanks. Gonna be getting my grub on
